# Local AstraNotes data store (never commit user notes / audit logs).
# NB: do not add a bare `AstraNotes/` rule — on case-insensitive filesystems it would
# also ignore the source package `src/astranotes/`. The store artifacts below suffice.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
audit.log
debug.log

